  {% if developer.validates == 'yes' %}<li>{% if developer.website %}<a href="{{ developer.website | url }}">{% endif %}{{ developer.name }}{% if developer.website %}</a>{% endif %}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
</ul>
<h2>Why Pledge?</h2>
<p>The pledge is a commitment to the craft of frontend development. <a href=/posts/2021/why-validate/><cite>Why Validate?</cite></a> outlines why validation is so important.
<h2>What Are the Conditions?</h2>
<ol>
  <li>You must be a frontend developer and it must be clear that you’re a frontend developer.
  <li>You pledge that you <a href=https://www.htmlvalidator.com/htmlval/whyvalidate.html>validate your HTML and CSS code</a>.
  <li>If you choose to add your website, you list your own website. Social media profiles are okay.
  <li>You acknowledge that there’s no right or entitlement to being or staying linked and listed.
</ol>